Module FloWeekTracker

Package com.floweektracker.model

package com.floweektracker.model
Model package contains classes that represent the data used in the application. These classes help to store and organize information for the planner and other parts of the program.

Class overview:

  • PanelNames - an enum representing the names of the main panels
  • SingleTask - represents a single task in the planner
  • WeekDays - an enum representing the days of the week
